description: Adam And The Ants - Stand And Deliver (The Very Best Of) [2007] DVD9 Adam and the Ants were an English rock band active during the late 1970s and early 1980s. The group, which lasted from 1977 to 1982 was fronted by Adam Ant. His greatest UK chart success was Adam & the Ants' 1980 album Kings of the Wild Frontier which was number one in the UK Albums Chart for a total of twelve weeks.
